headline: KeyBanc Raises First Solar (FSLR) Price Target After Mixed Earnings and Lower FY25 Outlook
summary: First Solar, Inc. (NASDAQ:FSLR) ranks among the best sustainability stocks to invest in. Despite announcing record quarterly volume and a solid third-quarter performance, First Solar, Inc. (NASDAQ:FSLR) released dismal full-year guidance on October 30. The company announced revenue of $1.59 billion, which narrowly exceeded the average estimate of $1.58 billion.
